                    <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold">Let's Compare</h2>
                    <p class="mb-5 font-light sm:text-xl">Discover a curated selection of vehicles meticulously chosen to cater to a spectrum of everyday lifestyles, spanning from families to tradespeople such as carpenters and civil workers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-6 xl:gap-10 lg:space-y-0">
                    <!-- Pricing Card -->
                    <div class="flex flex-col p-6 mx-auto max-w-lg text-center rounded-lg outline">
                        <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Tesla Model S</h3>
                        <p class="font-light">Best option for personal use & small families.</p>
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-baseline my-8">
                            <span class="mr-2 text-5xl font-extrabold">$74,990
                            </span>
                            <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"></span>
                        </div>
                        <!-- List -->
                        <ul role="list" class="mb-8 space-y-4 text-left">
                            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
